OL,6,FBy Hannah Ward-Glenton, ITV News
OL,7,FProducer
OL,9,FMurrieta Police Department in has a
OL,10,Fcreative way of dealing with the
OL,11,Fstate's new suspect identity laws:
OL,12,FLego heads.
OL,14,FA series of faces deftly disguise the
OL,15,Fpossible perpetrators on the
OL,16,FDepartment's social media accounts.
OL,18,FTheir identities are masked with faces
OL,19,Fexpressing an array of emotions, from
OL,20,Fa toothy grin to frowny tears.
