OL,3,CA Lego lineup: How a US police team
OL,4,Cworks around suspect identity laws
OL,6,FIt comes after a new law went into
OL,7,Feffect at the beginning of 2024 that
OL,8,Frestricts the how and when law
OL,9,Fenforcement agencies in California
OL,10,Fshare suspect photos and mugshots.
OL,12,F"The Murrieta Police Department prides
OL,13,Fitself in its transparency with the
OL,14,Fcommunity, but also honors everyone's
OL,15,Frights & protections as afforded by
OL,16,Flaw; even suspects," the police
OL,17,Fdepartment wrote on its, in a post
OL,18,Fexplaining the appearance of the
OL,19,Fyellow bricks.
