OL,3,CA Lego lineup: How a US police team
OL,4,Cworks around suspect identity laws
OL,6,F"In order to share what is happening
OL,7,Fin Murrieta, we chose to cover the
OL,8,Ffaces of suspects to protect their
OL,9,Fidentity while still aligning with the
OL,10,Fnew law."
OL,12,FThe new law came into place on January
OL,13,F1 and prohibits law enforcement from
OL,14,Fsharing suspect photos for non-violent
OL,15,Fcrimes.
OL,17,FThe rule also requires agencies to
OL,18,Fremove suspect mugshots from social
OL,19,Fmedia after 14 days, except for in
OL,20,Fspecial circumstances.
